{
  "video_id": "6LmPq7D-ds0",
  "title": "The real harm of the global arms trade | Samantha Nutt",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12727.0,
      "end_time": 14358.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much. Good evening."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14382.0,
      "end_time": 17698.0,
      "text": "Some of you may have noticed that my last name is Nutt."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18336.0,
      "end_time": 21139.0,
      "text": "And if you did, you are forgiven for wondering"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21163.0,
      "end_time": 24790.0,
      "text": "how a Nutt managed to end up in a war zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24103.0,
      "end_time": 28444.0,
      "text": "I actually was offered, right out of medical school, and accepted"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28468.0,
      "end_time": 32305.0,
      "text": "a volunteer contract to work with UNICEF in war-torn Somalia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32329.0,
      "end_time": 34808.0,
      "text": "that was worth one dollar."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34832.0,
      "end_time": 37243.0,
      "text": "And, you see, I had to be paid this dollar"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37267.0,
      "end_time": 40402.0,
      "text": "in the event that the UN needed to issue an evacuation order,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40426.0,
      "end_time": 42496.0,
      "text": "so that I would be covered."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42520.0,
      "end_time": 46892.0,
      "text": "I was, after all, heading into one of the world&#39;s most dangerous places."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47340.0,
      "end_time": 50475.0,
      "text": "And by now, some of you may be asking yourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50499.0,
      "end_time": 52310.0,
      "text": "and I just want to reassure you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52550.0,
      "end_time": 54354.0,
      "text": "that I did get half the money up front."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54378.0,
      "end_time": 56166.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56717.0,
      "end_time": 59568.0,
      "text": "But you see, this is how, with 50 cents in my pocket,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59593.0,
      "end_time": 61885.0,
      "text": "I ended up in Baidoa, Somalia."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62615.0,
      "end_time": 64885.0,
      "text": "Journalists called it the \"city of death.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65299.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67123.0,
      "text": "And they called it the city of death"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67147.0,
      "end_time": 70305.0,
      "text": "because 300,000 people had lost their lives there --"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70765.0,
      "end_time": 74363.0,
      "text": "300,000 people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74387.0,
      "end_time": 78543.0,
      "text": "mostly as a result of war-related famine and disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79487.0,
      "end_time": 83434.0,
      "text": "I was part of a team that was tasked with trying to figure out"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 83458.0,
      "end_time": 86426.0,
      "text": "how best to respond to this humanitarian catastrophe."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 86839.0,
      "end_time": 89554.0,
      "text": "It was right on the heels of the Rwandan genocide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 89578.0,
      "end_time": 92245.0,
      "text": "and aid money to the region was drying up."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 92269.0,
      "end_time": 94311.0,
      "text": "Many aid organizations, unfortunately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94335.0,
      "end_time": 96910.0,
      "text": "had been forced to close their doors."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96935.0,
      "end_time": 100645.0,
      "text": "And so the question that I was asked to specifically help answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100669.0,
      "end_time": 106345.0,
      "text": "which is one that aid workers ask themselves in war zones the world over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 107202.0,
      "end_time": 109250.0,
      "text": "is: What the hell do we do now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 110131.0,
      "end_time": 113535.0,
      "text": "You know, the security environment in Somalia at that moment in time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 113559.0,
      "end_time": 115590.0,
      "text": "and nothing has really changed too much --"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 115614.0,
      "end_time": 120520.0,
      "text": "can best be described as \"Mad Max\" by way of \"A Clockwork Orange.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 121477.0,
      "end_time": 126608.0,
      "text": "And I remember very distinctly a couple of days after my arrival,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 126632.0,
      "end_time": 129237.0,
      "text": "I went up to a feeding clinic."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 129967.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132505.0,
      "text": "There were dozens of women who were standing in line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 132529.0,
      "end_time": 135269.0,
      "text": "and they were clutching their infants very close."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 136309.0,
      "end_time": 139540.0,
      "text": "About 20 minutes into this conversation I was having"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 139780.0,
      "end_time": 141102.0,
      "text": "with this one young woman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 141126.0,
      "end_time": 142502.0,
      "text": "I leaned forward"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 143260.0,
      "end_time": 146796.0,
      "text": "and tried to put my finger in the palm of her baby&#39;s hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 148225.0,
      "end_time": 149536.0,
      "text": "And when I did this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 149560.0,
      "end_time": 153558.0,
      "text": "I discovered that her baby was already in rigor."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 154249.0,
      "end_time": 156300.0,
      "text": "She was stiff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 156709.0,
      "end_time": 160114.0,
      "text": "and her little, lifeless hand was curled into itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 160986.0,
      "end_time": 164530.0,
      "text": "She had died hours before"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 164759.0,
      "end_time": 166946.0,
      "text": "of malnutrition and dehydration."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 168242.0,
      "end_time": 171140.0,
      "text": "I later learned that as her baby was dying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 171164.0,
      "end_time": 175486.0,
      "text": "this young woman had been held for two days"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 175510.0,
      "end_time": 180245.0,
      "text": "by some teenage boys who were armed with Kalashnikov rifles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 180270.0,
      "end_time": 182800.0,
      "text": "and they were trying to shake her down for more money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 182824.0,
      "end_time": 185506.0,
      "text": "money she very clearly did not have."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 185807.0,
      "end_time": 189148.0,
      "text": "And this is a scene that I have confronted"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 189172.0,
      "end_time": 191759.0,
      "text": "in war zones the world over;"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 192435.0,
      "end_time": 197748.0,
      "text": "places where kids, some as young as eight -- they are this big --"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 198345.0,
      "end_time": 200668.0,
      "text": "and those kids, they have never been to school."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 201490.0,
      "end_time": 207121.0,
      "text": "But they have fought and they have killed with automatic rifles."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 208589.0,
      "end_time": 211502.0,
      "text": "Is this just the way the world is?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 212451.0,
      "end_time": 216799.0,
      "text": "Some will you tell you that war is unavoidably human."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 217234.0,
      "end_time": 220347.0,
      "text": "After all, it is as old as existence itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 221419.0,
      "end_time": 228530.0,
      "text": "We say never again, and yet it happens again and again and again."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 229232.0,
      "end_time": 234963.0,
      "text": "But I will tell you that I have seen the absolute worst"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 235671.0,
      "end_time": 239444.0,
      "text": "of what we as human beings are capable of doing to one another,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 240222.0,
      "end_time": 244627.0,
      "text": "and yet I still believe a different outcome is possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 245659.0,
      "end_time": 246893.0,
      "text": "Do you want to know why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 247536.0,
      "end_time": 249854.0,
      "text": "Because over 20 years of doing this work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 249878.0,
      "end_time": 252589.0,
      "text": "going in and out of war zones around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 252613.0,
      "end_time": 254756.0,
      "text": "I have come to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 254780.0,
      "end_time": 256700.0,
      "text": "that there are aspects of this problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 256724.0,
      "end_time": 260801.0,
      "text": "that we, all of us, as people occupying this shared space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 261421.0,
      "end_time": 263604.0,
      "text": "that we can change --"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 263628.0,
      "end_time": 267562.0,
      "text": "not through force or coercion or invasion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 267586.0,
      "end_time": 271315.0,
      "text": "but by simply looking at all of the options available to us"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 271940.0,
      "end_time": 277580.0,
      "text": "and choosing the ones that favor peace at the expense of war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 277722.0,
      "end_time": 281924.0,
      "text": "instead of war at the expense of peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 283158.0,
      "end_time": 284420.0,
      "text": "How so?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 284444.0,
      "end_time": 286183.0,
      "text": "Well, I want you to consider this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 286207.0,
      "end_time": 291664.0,
      "text": "there are at least 800 million small arms and light weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 291688.0,
      "end_time": 294144.0,
      "text": "in circulation in the world today."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 294788.0,
      "end_time": 298277.0,
      "text": "The vast majority of civilians, like that young baby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 298301.0,
      "end_time": 300690.0,
      "text": "who are dying in war zones around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 300714.0,
      "end_time": 303689.0,
      "text": "are dying at the hands of various armed groups"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 303713.0,
      "end_time": 310390.0,
      "text": "who rely on a near-infinite supply of cheap, easy and efficient weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 310630.0,
      "end_time": 314723.0,
      "text": "to rape, threaten, intimidate and brutalize those civilians"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 314747.0,
      "end_time": 316151.0,
      "text": "at every turn."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 316937.0,
      "end_time": 318880.0,
      "text": "How cheap?"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 318112.0,
      "end_time": 319728.0,
      "text": "Well, in some parts of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 319752.0,
      "end_time": 324150.0,
      "text": "you can buy an AK-47 for as little as 10 dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 324174.0,
      "end_time": 327300.0,
      "text": "In many places in which I have worked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 327621.0,
      "end_time": 332118.0,
      "text": "it is easier to get access to an automatic rifle"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 332142.0,
      "end_time": 336263.0,
      "text": "than it is to get access to clean drinking water."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 337400.0,
      "end_time": 338636.0,
      "text": "And so now the important part:"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 339699.0,
      "end_time": 342818.0,
      "text": "Can anything be done about this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 343922.0,
      "end_time": 345802.0,
      "text": "To answer that question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 345826.0,
      "end_time": 347836.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s take a look at this map of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 348246.0,
      "end_time": 352630.0,
      "text": "And now, let&#39;s add in all of the countries that are currently at war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 353266.0,
      "end_time": 355600.0,
      "text": "and the number of people who have either died"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 355624.0,
      "end_time": 358920.0,
      "text": "or have been displaced as a result of that violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 358116.0,
      "end_time": 359512.0,
      "text": "It is a staggering number --"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 359536.0,
      "end_time": 362233.0,
      "text": "more than 40 million people."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 362764.0,
      "end_time": 365431.0,
      "text": "But you will also notice something else about this map."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 365455.0,
      "end_time": 367575.0,
      "text": "You will notice that most of those countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 367599.0,
      "end_time": 368953.0,
      "text": "are in the Global South."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 369453.0,
      "end_time": 371743.0,
      "text": "Now, let&#39;s look at the countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 371767.0,
      "end_time": 376622.0,
      "text": "that are the world&#39;s top 20 exporters of small arms in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 377559.0,
      "end_time": 378801.0,
      "text": "And what do we notice?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 379331.0,
      "end_time": 380794.0,
      "text": "Well, you see them in green."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 380818.0,
      "end_time": 384707.0,
      "text": "You will notice that those are mostly countries in the Global North,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 384732.0,
      "end_time": 386430.0,
      "text": "primarily Western countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 386454.0,
      "end_time": 387670.0,
      "text": "What does this tell us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 387694.0,
      "end_time": 391185.0,
      "text": "This tells us that most of the people who are dying in war"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 391209.0,
      "end_time": 393112.0,
      "text": "are living in poor countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 393136.0,
      "end_time": 395950.0,
      "text": "and yet most of the people who are profiting from war"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 396609.0,
      "end_time": 400971.0,
      "text": "are living in rich countries -- people like you and me."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 401804.0,
      "end_time": 404606.0,
      "text": "And then what if we go beyond small arms for a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 404630.0,
      "end_time": 407854.0,
      "text": "What if we look at all weapons in circulation in the world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 407878.0,
      "end_time": 409662.0,
      "text": "Who does the biggest business?"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 409686.0,
      "end_time": 412161.0,
      "text": "Well, roughly 80 percent of those weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 412185.0,
      "end_time": 415727.0,
      "text": "come from none other than the five permanent members"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 415751.0,
      "end_time": 417642.0,
      "text": "of the United Nations Security Council,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 417666.0,
      "end_time": 419940.0,
      "text": "plus Germany."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 419769.0,
      "end_time": 421470.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s shocking, isn&#39;t it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 421515.0,
      "end_time": 424191.0,
      "text": "Now, some of you might be saying at this moment in time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 424215.0,
      "end_time": 427465.0,
      "text": "\"Oh yeah, but OK, hang on a second there ... Nutt.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 427490.0,
      "end_time": 429695.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 430267.0,
      "end_time": 432800.0,
      "text": "Grade school was spectacular for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 432104.0,
      "end_time": 434480.0,
      "text": "It was, really, a wonderful experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 434720.0,
      "end_time": 437260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 437420.0,
      "end_time": 439262.0,
      "text": "But you might be saying to yourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 439286.0,
      "end_time": 442634.0,
      "text": "You know, all of these weapons in war zones -- they&#39;re not a cause,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 442658.0,
      "end_time": 445800.0,
      "text": "but an effect of the violence that plagues them"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 445104.0,
      "end_time": 446587.0,
      "text": "each and every single day."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 446612.0,
      "end_time": 448795.0,
      "text": "You know, places like Iraq and Afghanistan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 448819.0,
      "end_time": 452233.0,
      "text": "where they need these weapons to be able to maintain law and order,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 452257.0,
      "end_time": 455878.0,
      "text": "promote peace and security, to combat terror groups --"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 455902.0,
      "end_time": 458397.0,
      "text": "surely this is a good thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 458773.0,
      "end_time": 461461.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take a look at that assumption for just one moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 461485.0,
      "end_time": 465271.0,
      "text": "because you see there has been a boom in the small-arms trade"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 465295.0,
      "end_time": 467790.0,
      "text": "since the start of the War on Terror."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 467103.0,
      "end_time": 470301.0,
      "text": "In fact, it is a business that has grown threefold"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 470325.0,
      "end_time": 472268.0,
      "text": "over the past 15 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 472688.0,
      "end_time": 476245.0,
      "text": "And now let&#39;s compare that to the number of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 476269.0,
      "end_time": 480950.0,
      "text": "who have directly died in armed conflict around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 480119.0,
      "end_time": 481294.0,
      "text": "in that same period."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 481627.0,
      "end_time": 483720.0,
      "text": "What do you notice?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 483960.0,
      "end_time": 485453.0,
      "text": "Well, you notice that, in fact, that also goes up"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 485477.0,
      "end_time": 487870.0,
      "text": "roughly three- to fourfold."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 487112.0,
      "end_time": 490777.0,
      "text": "They basically go up and end at the same point."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 491310.0,
      "end_time": 494800.0,
      "text": "Now, we can have a circular argument here"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 494104.0,
      "end_time": 498176.0,
      "text": "about whether this increase in fatalities is a response"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 498200.0,
      "end_time": 502109.0,
      "text": "to the increase of small arms, or the other way around."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 502133.0,
      "end_time": 504628.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s what we should really take away from this."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 504653.0,
      "end_time": 506313.0,
      "text": "What we should take away from this"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 506337.0,
      "end_time": 510755.0,
      "text": "is that this is a relationship worth scrutinizing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 511447.0,
      "end_time": 516313.0,
      "text": "especially when you consider that small arms that were shipped to Iraq"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 516337.0,
      "end_time": 518131.0,
      "text": "for use by the Iraqi Army,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 518155.0,
      "end_time": 521401.0,
      "text": "or to Syria for so-called moderate opposition fighters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 521426.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525619.0,
      "text": "that those arms, many of them, are now in the hands of ISIS;"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 526960.0,
      "end_time": 528836.0,
      "text": "or when you consider that arms that were shipped to Libya"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 528860.0,
      "end_time": 531573.0,
      "text": "are now actively drifting across the Sahel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 531597.0,
      "end_time": 536340.0,
      "text": "and ending up with groups like Boko Haram and al Qaeda"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 536364.0,
      "end_time": 539690.0,
      "text": "and other militant groups."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 539950.0,
      "end_time": 541784.0,
      "text": "And therein lies the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 542466.0,
      "end_time": 543618.0,
      "text": "Because, you see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 543642.0,
      "end_time": 549161.0,
      "text": "small arms anywhere are a menace everywhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 549831.0,
      "end_time": 554174.0,
      "text": "because their first stop is rarely their last."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 554904.0,
      "end_time": 557320.0,
      "text": "Spending on war per person per year"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 557344.0,
      "end_time": 561389.0,
      "text": "now amounts to about 249 dollars --"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 561413.0,
      "end_time": 563814.0,
      "text": "249 dollars per person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 563838.0,
      "end_time": 568776.0,
      "text": "which is roughly 12 times what we spend on foreign aid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 568801.0,
      "end_time": 572238.0,
      "text": "money that is used to educate and vaccinate children"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 572262.0,
      "end_time": 575125.0,
      "text": "and combat malnutrition in the Global South."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 575814.0,
      "end_time": 579111.0,
      "text": "But we can shift that balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 579604.0,
      "end_time": 580755.0,
      "text": "How do we do this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 580779.0,
      "end_time": 583621.0,
      "text": "Well, it is essentially a problem of both supply and demand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 583645.0,
      "end_time": 585588.0,
      "text": "so we can tackle it from both sides."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 585993.0,
      "end_time": 587663.0,
      "text": "On the supply side,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 587687.0,
      "end_time": 590861.0,
      "text": "we can push our governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 590885.0,
      "end_time": 593948.0,
      "text": "to adopt international arms transparency mechanisms"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 593972.0,
      "end_time": 595773.0,
      "text": "like the Arms Trade Treaty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 595797.0,
      "end_time": 599564.0,
      "text": "which makes it so that rich countries have to be more accountable"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 599588.0,
      "end_time": 601262.0,
      "text": "for where their arms are going"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 601287.0,
      "end_time": 603686.0,
      "text": "and what their arms might be used for."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 603710.0,
      "end_time": 604975.0,
      "text": "Here in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 604999.0,
      "end_time": 609616.0,
      "text": "the largest arms-exporting country in the world by far,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 609640.0,
      "end_time": 613564.0,
      "text": "President Obama has rightly signed the Arms Trade Treaty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 613589.0,
      "end_time": 616150.0,
      "text": "but none of it takes effect, it isn&#39;t binding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 616174.0,
      "end_time": 619683.0,
      "text": "until it is approved and ratified by the Senate."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 620865.0,
      "end_time": 623819.0,
      "text": "This is where we need to make our voices heard."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 623843.0,
      "end_time": 627557.0,
      "text": "You know, the curbing of small arms --"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 627581.0,
      "end_time": 630383.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not going to solve the problem of war."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 630407.0,
      "end_time": 633689.0,
      "text": "Increased control mechanisms won&#39;t solve that problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 633713.0,
      "end_time": 636959.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s an important step in the right direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 636984.0,
      "end_time": 639857.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s up to all of us who live in those rich countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 639881.0,
      "end_time": 641690.0,
      "text": "to make change here."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 641994.0,
      "end_time": 645203.0,
      "text": "What about on the demand side?"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 645227.0,
      "end_time": 647980.0,
      "text": "You know, there are generations around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 648400.0,
      "end_time": 650600.0,
      "text": "who are being lost to war."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 651202.0,
      "end_time": 654193.0,
      "text": "It is possible to disrupt that cycle of violence"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 654217.0,
      "end_time": 658210.0,
      "text": "with investments in education, in strengthening the rule of law"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 658234.0,
      "end_time": 660615.0,
      "text": "and in economic development, especially for women."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 660639.0,
      "end_time": 662267.0,
      "text": "I have personally seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 662291.0,
      "end_time": 665332.0,
      "text": "just how incredibly powerful those kinds of efforts can be"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 665356.0,
      "end_time": 666689.0,
      "text": "around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 667458.0,
      "end_time": 668834.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s the thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 668858.0,
      "end_time": 670266.0,
      "text": "they take time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 670290.0,
      "end_time": 674329.0,
      "text": "which means for you as individuals, if you want to give,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 674353.0,
      "end_time": 676600.0,
      "text": "please, by all means do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 676840.0,
      "end_time": 679646.0,
      "text": "But know that how you give is just as important"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 679671.0,
      "end_time": 681678.0,
      "text": "as how much you give."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 682147.0,
      "end_time": 684592.0,
      "text": "Regular contributions like monthly contributions"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 684616.0,
      "end_time": 687904.0,
      "text": "are a far more effective way of giving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 687928.0,
      "end_time": 690641.0,
      "text": "because they allow humanitarian organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 690665.0,
      "end_time": 694990.0,
      "text": "to properly plan and be invested over the long term,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 695140.0,
      "end_time": 700639.0,
      "text": "and to be present in the lives of families who have been affected by war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 700663.0,
      "end_time": 704899.0,
      "text": "wars that many of us, frankly, all too quickly forget."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 705939.0,
      "end_time": 711299.0,
      "text": "When I first got on that plane for Somalia as a young doctor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 712942.0,
      "end_time": 716239.0,
      "text": "I had no idea what it meant to live with war."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 717519.0,
      "end_time": 719921.0,
      "text": "But I can tell you that I know what it means now."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 720636.0,
      "end_time": 722981.0,
      "text": "And I know what it means"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 723529.0,
      "end_time": 727704.0,
      "text": "to lie in bed in the pitch-black night"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 728684.0,
      "end_time": 732327.0,
      "text": "and listen to that haunting \"pop-pop-pop-pop-pop!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 733295.0,
      "end_time": 734914.0,
      "text": "of automatic gunfire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 736200.0,
      "end_time": 738425.0,
      "text": "and wonder with absolute dread"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 739298.0,
      "end_time": 742885.0,
      "text": "how many minutes I have left until it will be right on top of me."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 743556.0,
      "end_time": 748593.0,
      "text": "I can tell you that it is a terrifying and agonizing fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 748617.0,
      "end_time": 752973.0,
      "text": "one that millions of people around the world are forced to confront"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 752998.0,
      "end_time": 755164.0,
      "text": "each and every single day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 755188.0,
      "end_time": 756521.0,
      "text": "especially children."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 757417.0,
      "end_time": 760157.0,
      "text": "Over the years of doing this work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 760181.0,
      "end_time": 765293.0,
      "text": "unfortunately, war has killed far too many people close to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 766277.0,
      "end_time": 769253.0,
      "text": "And on at least a couple of occasions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 769277.0,
      "end_time": 772470.0,
      "text": "war has very nearly killed me as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 773309.0,
      "end_time": 778183.0,
      "text": "But I firmly believe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 778207.0,
      "end_time": 780984.0,
      "text": "which is why I get up and do what I do every single day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 781786.0,
      "end_time": 784513.0,
      "text": "that we can make different choices here."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 785284.0,
      "end_time": 788103.0,
      "text": "Because you see, war is ours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 788127.0,
      "end_time": 789705.0,
      "text": "as human beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 789730.0,
      "end_time": 793342.0,
      "text": "We buy it, sell it, spread it and wage it."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 793960.0,
      "end_time": 797659.0,
      "text": "We are therefore not powerless to solve it."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 798569.0,
      "end_time": 800240.0,
      "text": "On the contrary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 800264.0,
      "end_time": 803215.0,
      "text": "we are the only ones who can."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 803731.0,
      "end_time": 806841.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much, and I want to wish you the greatest success."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 806865.0,
      "end_time": 813739.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}